<TEXT>
<P>
 Although in some ways as capable as its ex-Marine/ex-CIA hero (played by 
Harrison Ford, pictured), this 1992 release could use more of this gentleman's 
moxie.The second of techno-master Tom Clancy's novels to be filmed, it's a 
