<HEADLINE>
<P>
MY BEST SHOT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A family reunion drew Carolyn Frank of Mission Viejo back to Hawaii last 
fall.The Hawaii-born Frank was with her parents in Lahaina, Maui -- a spot they 
hadn't visited in a while -- and they were taking an early morning stroll. "I 
peeked in the door of a little seaside shop and was immediately struck by what 
I call the 'Cavalcade of Hats,' " says Frank, a schoolteacher and avid amateur 
photographer. "It was one of those quirk shots. You might take 50 or a hundred 
pictures and one turns out to be great." 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041794-0089 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 032997 </DOCID>
