</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
A NOTE TO READERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Last Sunday's cover story on Courtney Love drew some angry letters and 
calls.Most accused Calendar of insensitivity for publishing the story two days 
after the news broke that Love's husband, Kurt Cobain of the rock group 
Nirvana, had committed suicide at the couple's Seattle home. 
</P>
<P>
 Sunday Calendar is printed Thursday and early Friday, along with some other 
sections of the Sunday paper. As a result, last week's section was printed and 
on its way to distributors when news reached us of Cobain's tragic death. 
</P>
</TEXT>
