<P>
CIVILIANS ATTACK MILITARY ROADBLOCK IN CHIAPAS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A band of gunmen assaulted a military roadblock near the Chiapas state capital 
of Tuxtla Gutierrez Friday and one soldier died in the hourlong shootout, 
Mexico's defense ministry said. 
</P>
<P>
 It was not known if the attackers, who fled into the surrounding hills, 
