<HEADLINE>
<P>
JAPANESE STUDENT SHOT IN CARJACKING ATTEMPT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Japanese college student was shot in the chest early Friday in what police 
say was a carjacking. 
</P>
<P>
 Police said two men confronted Kouichi Takamoto, 26, about 1 a.m., shot him in 
the chest and stole his 1987 white Toyota. 
