<HEADLINE>
<P>
AGENTS SEIZE $9 MILLION IN ILLEGAL DRUG PROCEEDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 U.S. customs agents seized more than $9 million in illegal drug proceeds 
before they could be smuggled from Miami to Colombia, officials said Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 The total amount -- $9,117,960 in cash -- was hidden in 53 stereo speakers and 
