</P>
<P>
 Alemany 14, Harvard-Westlake 6 -- Jon Tucker drove in three runs for Alemany 
(13-6, 4-2) in a Mission League game. 
</P>
<P>
 Chaminade 6, St. Bernard 1 -- Gabe Crecion pitched six strong innings and hit 
a three-run home run as Chaminade won a Mission League game. Kevin Lohman and 
