<DOCNO> LA041794-0289 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 033197 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 17, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 8; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
