president of the new commercial mortgage finance division. Swon was previously 
managing director of the commercial real estate finance division of Equitable 
Life Insurance Co. of Iowa. Before that, he was vice president of the 
structured finance group of Merrill Lynch Capital Markets Inc. in Los Angeles. 
</P>
