<P>
MOTORIST KILLED IN CRASH IS IDENTIFIED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Police have identified a motorist who was killed Friday in a head-on collision 
on Lassen Street as Mohibullah Helmandi 27, of Granada Hills. 
</P>
<P>
 Helmandi may have been trying to control a nosebleed when his car veered to 
the wrong side of the street and struck a pickup truck in the 18500 block of 
Lassen Street, said Officer Ralph Kemptner of the Los Angeles Police 
Department's Valley Traffic Division. 
</P>
<P>
 The driver of the truck, Jeffrey Ault, 33, of Sepulveda, was not seriously 
injured. 
</P>
<P>
 Police are still investigating the accident. 
