<P>
 BOYS' VOLLEYBALL 
</P>
<P>
 Bell upset host Roosevelt in consecutive games, 15-13, 15-4, 15-9, last week 
in a Southeastern Conference match that could determine the conference title. 
</P>
<P>
 It was the first time in four years that the Eagles have beaten the 
Roughriders. 
</P>
<P>
 Bell senior middle attacker Ricardo Lopez finished with 15 blocks and 19 
kills, including five kills behind the 10-foot line. ENRIQUE LAVIN 
